OL,3,CPep Guardiola to hold talks over
OL,4,CManchester City future
OL,6,FPep Guardiola plans to hold urgent
OL,7,Ftalks with Manchester City chairman
OL,8,FKhaldoon Al Mubarak regarding his
OL,9,Ffuture, amid growing reports that he
OL,10,Fwill leave the club at the end of the
OL,11,Fseason.
OL,13,FThe news comes as Arsenal were
OL,14,Fofficially crowned Premier League
OL,15,Fchampions for the first time in 22
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
