OL,3,CPep Guardiola to hold talks over
OL,4,CManchester City future
OL,6,FSecond-placed Manchester City failed
OL,7,Fto take the title race to the final
OL,8,Fday of the season following a 1-1 draw
OL,9,Fon Tuesday, 19 May, against a Europe-
OL,10,Fbound Bournemouth side.
OL,12,FBuild-up to the must-win game on the
OL,13,Fsouth coast was dominated by news of
OL,14,FGuardiola's possible summer departure,
OL,15,Fwith Enzo Maresca rumoured to be his
OL,16,Fpotential successor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779279069
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to hold talks over
OL,4,CManchester City future
OL,6,FThe City manager, who has a year
OL,7,Fremaining on his contract, refused to
OL,8,Fclarify the situation as he turns his
OL,9,Fattention to Sunday's season finale at
OL,10,Fhome to Aston Villa.
OL,12,F"With the club, I always talk but not
OL,13,Fnow," said Guardiola. "Three, four
OL,14,Fseasons ago when there was one year
OL,15,Fleft, the first thing you have to
OL,16,Funderstand, I should talk with my
OL,17,Fchairman first.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@EO]uD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779279069
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to hold talks over
OL,4,CManchester City future
OL,6,F"And when I talk with my chairman, we
OL,7,F(may) decide to have one more year, we
OL,8,Fwill talk (about) everything and we
OL,9,Fwill decide. We (will) talk in the
OL,10,Fnext days."
OL,12,FCity arrived in Dorset seeking to keep
OL,13,Falive their pursuit of a domestic
OL,14,Ftreble after lifting the FA Cup just
OL,15,Fdays ago following Carabao Cup glory
OL,16,Fin March.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
