OL,3,CPep Guardiola to hold talks over
OL,4,CManchester City future
OL,6,FErling Haaland cancelled out Junior
OL,7,FKroupi's first-half opener in the
OL,8,Ffifth minute of added time but the
OL,9,Fvisitors were unable to force a last-
OL,10,Fgasp winner as Guardiola was denied a
OL,11,Fpotential fairytale farewell.
OL,13,FTravelling fans chanted "one more
OL,14,Fyear, one more year, Guardiola" during
OL,15,Fthe game, while one fan unfurled a
OL,16,Fbedsheet with 'Pep Stay' written on it.
OL,26,@uD@YOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779279069
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to hold talks over
OL,4,CManchester City future
OL,6,FWhen asked if rumours of his departure
OL,7,Fcould impact the team's performance,
OL,8,Fhe said: "I always said that when you
OL,9,Fare fighting for the titles or FA
OL,10,FCups, in the first moment there is a
OL,11,Fproblem the players don't follow you
OL,12,Fanymore.
OL,14,F"You have to stay there and I have to
OL,15,Ftalk with my chairman and I say 'let
OL,16,Fthe season go and when it will be over
OL,17,Fwe will talk'. But he deserves the
OL,18,Ffirst talk about what we have to do."
OL,20,FCity are now an unassailable four
OL,21,Fpoints adrift of table-topping Arsenal.
OL,26,@pD@JOUvD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
