OL,3,CPep Guardiola to hold talks over
OL,4,CManchester City future
OL,6,FGuardiola, who began his post-match
OL,7,Fpress conference by congratulating the
OL,8,FGunners and their manager Mikel
OL,9,FArteta, initially used the word "we"
OL,10,Fwhen asked about his club's future
OL,11,Fprospects, before saying "City".
OL,13,F"Next season, we will be back," said
OL,14,Fthe 55-year-old, who has won six
OL,15,FPremier League titles and the
OL,16,FChampions League during his 10-year
OL,17,Freign.
OL,26,@qD@aOUqD@dO]sD@ZOUsD@_O]uD@AOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779279069
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to hold talks over
OL,4,CManchester City future
OL,6,F"City will be back and we will try to
OL,7,Fbring the team in that sense:
OL,8,Fcompeting until the end in the
OL,9,Fcompetitions."
OL,11,FSixth-placed Bournemouth clinched
OL,12,Fcontinental qualification for the
OL,13,Ffirst time in the club's 127-year
OL,14,Fhistory after guaranteeing a top-seven
OL,15,Ffinish.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@NO]
